{"tid":497223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【神魔之塔】科大兩兄弟靠手遊發達 6,660萬買天賦海灣","createTime":"2017-12-12T13:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T07:44:51.000Z","uid":7262,"like":20,"dislike":175,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"89e529afd5982d1eb9cfc09a1601f1faadfa11ef","tid":497223,"uid":7262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171212/57573461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171212%2F57573461&d=d8xo9qgt%2FdGmG2m6pAbXi6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a82d1fd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171212%2F57573461&h=095b2af5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171212/57573461</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171212/large/1513080043_5f4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171212%2Flarge%2F1513080043_5f4a.jpg&h=99b5a74c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，大埔天賦海灣3座7樓A及B室，實用面積1,708方呎及1,720方呎，每單位連一個車位，各登記以3,330萬元易手，總價6,660萬元，兩伙平均呎價19,428元，登記買家分別為曾建中（Terry）及曾建豪，與港產手機遊戲《神魔之塔》創辦人兩兄弟同名，料為同一人。<br />\n<br />\n「80後」曾建中及曾建豪於2006年畢業於科大，兩兄弟開設的Madhead公司，2013年推出被指抄襲日本同類遊戲轉珠遊戲的《神魔之塔》，大受歡迎。2014年3月，內地遊戲開發商雲遊宣佈，斥資7,000萬美元（約5.4億港元）入股《神》的母公司Magic Feature兩成股權，曾建中及曾建豪兩兄弟，靠手遊App晉身億萬富豪。<br />\n曾建中原任銀行銷售員，月入四萬元，2008年中萌起創業計劃，「我想做自己想做嘅事」，其弟曾建豪也放棄月入三萬元的資訊科技工作，一同創業。他用六萬元儲蓄起家，編寫了一個電子卡網站，「18個月都冇收入，銀行戶口剩番9.96蚊，連最後100蚊都㩒埋出嚟。」"},{"pid":"1b6cae9aacfc95e999c0f5017758d5c60016948d","tid":497223,"uid":9193,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:56:28.000Z","msg":"而家仲有人玩咩"},{"pid":"ba7fb2e1317358d365bb1b674823224b22ce3bc6","tid":497223,"uid":38461,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:57:23.000Z","msg":